Example AirSensor Timeseries dataset

Source: R/data.R
example_sensor_scaqmd.Rd

The example_sensor_scaqmd dataset provides a quickly loadable version of a multi-sensor airsensor object for practicing and code examples. This dataset was was generated on 2020-09-15 by running:

library(AirSensor)

setArchiveBaseUrl("http://data.mazamascience.com/PurpleAir/v1")

example_sensor_scaqmd <-
  sensor_load("scaqmd", startdate = 20190701, enddate = 20190708)

save(example_sensor_scaqmd, file = "data/example_sensor_scaqmd.rda")

example_sensor_scaqmd

Format

An S3 object composed of "meta" and "data" data.
